Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pale broken wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:01.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are just a bit tired from\Nthat clear blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.32,0:00:06.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to force\Nyour smiles for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.60,0:00:13.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now... to smile for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.04,0:00:18.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Loneliness still continues to stalk me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.00,0:00:21.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A candle lit within
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.68,0:00:25.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The party is lively;\Nthe chandeliers are gorgeous, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.20,0:00:32.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I fill the hole left behind\Nby those lacking words?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.64,0:00:35.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:42.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can at least swim freely\Nin my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:45.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't need a sky like that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.04,0:00:55.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can face tomorrow without painting\Nover all the things up to yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.48,0:00:59.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your pale broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.60,0:01:06.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are just a bit tired from\Nthat clear blue sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.12,0:01:12.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to force\Nyour smiles for someone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.28,0:01:18.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay now... to smile for yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.12,0:01:32.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.64,0:01:35.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the spiritual guardians\Nof the World of the Living.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.04,0:01:37.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are the balancers
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who keep a close eye\Non the countless souls,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.00,0:01:42.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,good and evil,\Nthat fill this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:47.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo and his friends manage\Nto defeat the Arrancar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:49.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who come to Karakura Town,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.44,0:01:51.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but they suffer a lot of damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.68,0:01:54.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been able to protect anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:57.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even been able\Nto bring down
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.44,0:01:58.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the one who hurt my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:02.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.48,0:02:06.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you knew\Nwhere we were, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo visited the Visoreds
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.16,0:02:13.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to learn how to suppress\Nhis inner Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You pass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:26.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to pound knowledge\Nof how to suppress your Hollow
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.24,0:02:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,all the way into the heart\Nof your soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:44.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while... King...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.60,0:02:48.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is old man Zangetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:50.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:53.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When you talk about Zangetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:55.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,are you talking about\Nthe one that you're holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:02:58.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it the one...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.40,0:03:05.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm holding?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:20.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Lisa Yadomaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.44,0:03:24.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.80,0:03:43.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ban...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.68,0:03:44.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...kai!\N- ...kai!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:53.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:11.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard... When did you learn\Nhow to use a Bankai?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.36,0:04:13.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.80,0:04:16.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The same moment that you did!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.28,0:04:27.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Soul Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.80,0:04:30.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.36,0:04:33.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.76,0:04:37.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter...Senbonzakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.60,0:04:44.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:46.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:49.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:50.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:54.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your power now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:56.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.32,0:04:59.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the world is happening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:01.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.76,0:05:05.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?!\NWhy have you shown up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.08,0:05:11.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've become rather pathetic,\NIchigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:12.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.80,0:05:17.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bankai...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.48,0:05:29.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.84,0:05:33.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Scatter!\NSenbonzakura Kageyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.76,0:05:36.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.00,0:05:46.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.08,0:05:49.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to\Nbe fighting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:00.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:05.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't even acknowledged\Nthe confusion in your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.28,0:06:07.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:10.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly did I do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.88,0:06:13.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up...Ichigo Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:16.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.80,0:06:25.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.20,0:06:29.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're being stubborn!\NWhat do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.16,0:07:18.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo Kurosaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.80,0:07:25.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that it is impossible\Nfor you to obtain a true Bankai.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.28,0:07:28.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:32.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the state of Bankai\Nright now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.20,0:07:36.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.52,0:07:58.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have no will to\Nfight cannot stop my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:00.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.64,0:08:15.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so annoyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:17.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.16,0:08:22.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.44,0:08:27.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that just now?\NWhy did Byakuya appear?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:30.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:34.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get careless at a time like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:36.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not getting careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.08,0:08:41.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With a look like that on your face,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.32,0:08:43.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,how can you say that\Nyou're not getting careless?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.52,0:08:47.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that I'm not getting careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:50.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.00,0:08:58.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He stopped it with one hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:06.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getsugatensho!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:23.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,2...1...\NThat makes ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hachi!\NTime to switch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:28.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Open it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:29.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:45.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time! Trade off!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:52.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kensei Muguruma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.52,0:09:56.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to crush you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:04.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't waste your time, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:10.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry,\Nhe'll really have to kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.80,0:10:20.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that\Nyou're really bad at this, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.16,0:10:29.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the one who used\Nthe Getsugatensho in Bankai first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.60,0:10:36.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You just copied the way I fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:39.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just an incompetent brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.36,0:10:42.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.00,0:10:47.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:55.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you\Nthat you really can't use...Bankai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:01.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really quite pathetic, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.44,0:11:03.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:10.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do I have to rest?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.08,0:11:24.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are eight of us in all,\Nand we're rotating,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.32,0:11:26.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so ten minutes times eight\Nis 80 minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:29.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It isn't "times eight," baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:31.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you exclude her, it's seven!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:35.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten minutes times seven\Nis 70 minutes then!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:44.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My job is to set the barrier,\Nbut I'm still included...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.60,0:11:50.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He was strong! Far more than\NI thought he would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.76,0:11:56.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Kensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.38,0:11:58.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:08.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instant Regeneration!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.60,0:12:16.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? He's pretty serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:19.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand the\Nsituation best, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.48,0:12:30.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.52,0:12:31.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.36,0:12:32.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.52,0:12:48.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,His Hollow transformation\Nis unexpectedly fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:55.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The maximum amount of time\Nhe can take in his Visored Training
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.68,0:12:58.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to control his Hollow transformation\Nis about one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:05.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Excluding Hachigen,\Nten minutes times six is 60 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.00,0:13:09.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That means that when\Nmy turn comes around again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:12.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.48,0:13:20.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kariya...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hallucination...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:28.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a hallucination!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:32.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.68,0:13:33.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.64,0:13:37.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The mind sees hallucinations...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.52,0:13:44.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since your mind created me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:50.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,it means that you're concerned\Nabout the fact that you defeated me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.56,0:13:56.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You always look back whenever\Nyou finish a battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.96,0:13:59.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You look at the foe you defeated
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:01.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the friends\Nyou couldn't protect.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.60,0:14:07.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you that afraid to move\Nforward through battle?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.88,0:14:11.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you afraid to walk\Nthe same path as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.20,0:14:13.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I'm not like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:21.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your Zangetsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.80,0:14:25.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that you can defeat me\Nwith your bare hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:37.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost your Zangetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:40.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how helpless you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:45.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as defenseless as\Na scared baby!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:47.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.92,0:14:49.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want a weapon that badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll give you one!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:09.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.68,0:15:14.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... It's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.76,0:15:19.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You want a weapon, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.32,0:15:21.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose whichever one you like...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.44,0:15:30.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.48,0:15:34.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zangetsu isn't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.32,0:15:37.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.56,0:15:40.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zangetsu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.76,0:15:44.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NAren't you going to take a weapon?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.12,0:15:48.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you going to repel this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.80,0:15:53.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's within me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.72,0:15:57.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Zangetsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.20,0:16:10.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you can't say whatever you like!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:14.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting a weapon has\Nmade you confident...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.04,0:16:17.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:19.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.76,0:16:21.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then cut me down with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.96,0:16:27.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You cannot cut me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:34.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...with that blade that regrets\Ncutting me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.68,0:16:40.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:44.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth about battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.64,0:16:49.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Battles go on forever...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you defeat one person,\Nanother strong person will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:59.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And even if you defeat him,\Nan even stronger person will appear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.72,0:17:03.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't have the determination
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:06.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to withstand that everlasting struggle,\Nyou will lose someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.20,0:17:09.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it doesn't end there...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.76,0:17:13.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else will repeat the battles.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:15.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a cycle of rebirth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.32,0:17:18.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not limited to the life\Nand death of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.12,0:17:19.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Battle has its own cycle of rebirth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.36,0:17:23.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as peoples' souls exist,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.64,0:17:26.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,conflicts will be born and\Nbattles will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:31.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Battles will repeat themselves\Nthroughout eternity!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're foolish!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:48.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those with power will always\Nbe drawn into battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.96,0:17:51.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It was the same for us Bounts...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.72,0:17:57.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones who are first to\Nlose their lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.92,0:17:59.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,are idealists like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.88,0:18:06.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:10.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still fighting with\Na weak blade like this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:14.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any pride?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.60,0:18:30.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Z-Zangetsu is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not Zangetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.92,0:18:38.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you that I'm Zangetsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.36,0:18:47.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As usual, you're amazingly stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:51.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've lost your weapon.\NWhy are you just standing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.28,0:18:53.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:58.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the difference between\Na king and his horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.84,0:18:59.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:03.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean, "one's a person\Nand the other's a horse,"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,or "one has two legs and\Nthe other has four."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.36,0:19:08.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not giving you a kid's riddle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.60,0:19:11.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Form, abilities, and power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.68,0:19:14.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the two were\Nexactly the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:17.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,one would be the king\Nwho controls the battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.88,0:19:20.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and the other would be the horse\Nthat lends its power to the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking you what the difference\Nis between them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.76,0:19:27.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's instinct!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:33.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the thing that someone\Nwith equal power needs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in order to gain even greater power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:38.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What someone needs to\Nbecome the king is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.88,0:19:43.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The desire to engage in battle,\Nand to obtain power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.68,0:19:47.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And the desire to mercilessly crush\Nand trample your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.76,0:19:50.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The absolute desire to\Nengage in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.48,0:19:56.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our sharp, murderous instincts\Nare etched deep
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.64,0:19:59.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in the core of our bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.64,0:20:05.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have no raw instinct!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:07.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You fight with reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.84,0:20:10.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You try to defeat your foes with reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.64,0:20:14.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who can you cut with\Na sheathed sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.16,0:20:21.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're weaker\Nthan I am, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:34.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want that, Ichigo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.44,0:20:38.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know about Zangetsu,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.56,0:20:41.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't want a king\Nwho's weaker than I am
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:45.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,to ride around on me and\Nget us both killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.80,0:20:51.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're weak, so I'll crush you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:57.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll become the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.12,0:21:04.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.52,0:21:09.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,To desire to engage in battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.84,0:21:13.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.64,0:21:16.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't give it to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.88,0:21:20.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,SWORD
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.28,0:21:20.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:43.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Instinct...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.64,0:21:54.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I dressed up my five fingers\Nwith a manicure
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.76,0:22:00.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And then what's glowing\Nwas me instead
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:03.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspiration is like a goldfish
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:06.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps a voice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:09.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no sound that\Ndoesn't bounce back
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.60,0:22:25.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those lines stretching parallel\Nto each other
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.16,0:22:31.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They say one line turns beautiful,\Nthen deteriorate repeatedly
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:36.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm standing right there, \Nbut the way is locked
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.64,0:22:40.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The distance grows, \Nbut it's within reach
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.20,0:22:41.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And even today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.08,0:22:51.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I trace your gibberish roman letters\Nover and over with my left hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.84,0:23:01.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The one you see the moment\Nyou open your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.52,0:23:11.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What color will\Nhe paint your nails?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:24.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo seems like he's having fun\Nin his internal battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.19,0:23:26.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you suppose\Nhe's having a really good dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.03,0:23:28.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Men always have perverted dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:31.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! When we're trying really hard\Nto help him! Tthat perverted baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.77,0:23:34.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Perverted baldy?! Perverted...\NPerverted baldy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.31,0:23:37.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Illustrated guide to Soul Reapers!\NGolden!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.81,0:23:39.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Kusajishi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.47,0:23:40.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.08,0:23:41.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.88,0:23:45.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Something amusing will happen
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.17,0:23:47.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if you put that in the mouth\Nof a stuffed animal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.06,0:23:47.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.38,0:23:52.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.57,0:23:53.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.26,0:23:59.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A dog manju!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:02.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? "Dog manju"?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.09,0:24:03.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,THE END
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over?!